sses. They hold the key to our livelihood and many fail to carry such great responsibility. Capitalism is eclipsing at the bond people used to develop with their masters and their servants.","_key":"095d2aa0f0dc0"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","_key":"f264b62a82f5"},{"markDefs":[],"children":[{"_key":"fe0d0e3623ee0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We are equipped with years of expertise with these age-old conflicts and are here to help you resolve some of the most feared lawsuits by American employers."}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","_key":"7ec6179a87f0"}],"_updatedAt":"2022-12-19T00:13:23Z","mainImage":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-afd266d59dc3ddcc2f06ab71fbccc207a466d257-3008x2000-jpg","_type":"reference"}},"title":"Labor and Employment Law"}],"bgImage":null,"description":null,"_type":"practiceareas","mainImage":null,"image1":null,"email":null,"name":null,"body":[{"_type":"block","style":"blockquote","_key":"2af75d5baa02","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_key":"709e991aecd80","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"“No one can feel free from danger and destruction until the many torn threads of civilization are bound together again. We cannot feel safer until every nation, regardless of weapons or power, will meet together in good faith, the people worthy of mutual association.”\n\nRuth Bader Ginsburg (The Notorious RBG)"}]}],"fax":null,"attorneys":null,"image2":null,"phone":null},{"phone":"+1 718 717 5513","bgImage":null,"title":"Get In Touch","description":null,"_type":"getintouch","image1":null,"image2":null,"fax":"+1 347 913 8676","attorneys":null,"slides":null,"body":[{"_type":"block","style":"normal","_key":"1e8e2c751150","markDefs":[],"children":[{"_key":"2a021aabcd0d0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Please let us know any questions and comments you may have by filling out the form below. Thank you and we look forward to working with you."}]}],"name":null,"mainImage":{"_type":"poster","attribution":"Unsplash","asset":{"_ref":"image-11de5d6a432